title: Dr. Darkness Halloween Wreath
description:
Dr. Darkness Halloween Wreath 
26" across
This is one of my favorite Halloween wreaths! If you like Halloween a little on the dark side than this is your wreath. I started by painting a grapevine wreath black. I then added mesh ribbons, purple roses, black eucalyptus, glittery black leaves, purple glitter picks & purple spiders. The best part is the skull and hands of this elegant witch doctor in his snazzy top hat.
